{"tid":1054173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 劉江去世","createTime":"2019-03-09T15:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T16:03:50.000Z","uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"844223d6e236421d7c1d387e6e556aa103941399","tid":1054173,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"【時尚集團董事長劉江先生因病去世】2019年3月9日，時尚集團創始人，董事長劉江先生突發疾病去世，享年62歲。1993年，劉江先生和吳泓先生聯手創立了中國歷史上第一本時尚雜誌 - 。&ldquo;時尚&rdquo;這一本雜誌經過26年慢慢發展為了今天的時尚傳媒集團直到今天，時尚傳媒集團傳媒旗下已經擁有12本雜誌品牌，頂峰之時到達過17本之多"},{"pid":"d0073ca1a84e458b947525b77976a800b98111d2","tid":1054173,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917b3c82f3d515676ceb6cd531e8da2448c4c2e1","tid":1054173,"uid":169994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:02:23.000Z","msg":"屌，講呢啲"},{"pid":"7b7357b526580387954df4fc800787c5a90fed9e","tid":1054173,"uid":41308,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T16:03:50.000Z","msg":"我仲以為係劉江華<br />\n屌"}]}